<br />\n貪有10個8個月 bonus<br />\n邊個估到當日狀元<br />\n今日會燒炭死<br />\n<br />\n真係永不做it 狗<br />\n伏到不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>依樣野有機會，但問題係班老屎忽根本唔撚識IT<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日懶醒<br />\n如果真係因為依個原因，其實都好on9，銀行依啲重要系統，幾十年時都唔會<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">換</span></span></strong>，靠住啲對個system熟悉既員工做maintenance，一用其他新仔，除時彎個系統損失幾憶到幾百億<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到時邊個負責</blockquote>"},{"pid":"5ba728622f6084c2438dda411096fe9a378357e1","tid":569460,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T01:21:43.000Z","msg":"想知邊間銀行 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4813378f375a6c22be24b43b28a114feb7f8ac98","tid":569460,"uid":54929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T01:25:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9fd6742bd7bb2cd132e517d091aefd18d0524c3","tid":569460,"uid":32380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T01:26:18.000Z","msg":"個個工種都有壓力日日都有人自殺㗎啦🤷&zwj;♀️"},{"pid":"931e1d4fe0997520853ac9ef900f005914d70578","tid":569460,"uid":98317,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c8204dd2615e929229755e9c959e9c4d549787e1","tid":569460,"uid":123711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T17:24:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T01:29:23.000Z","msg":"冇，就算係美國嗰邊都搞唔成，原本話統一認證搞個世界認可既software engineer 試，最後都搞唔成"},{"pid":"d7b61f0ac04697d0f1d448b474f3c280a1658494","tid":569460,"uid":54060,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1d0005586df45830a445cce5f78c178b388d06bb","tid":569460,"uid":84436,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T23:55:49.000Z","msg":"RIP,如果有得做政府工服務大眾可能仲好,壓力低點<br />\n<br />\n畢業時 ACO(政府工既文員-助理文書主任) IT(support,infra,si,coder)<br />\nACO: 起薪近14.XK <br />\nIT\t:IVE/UGRAD 平均 1X K<br />\n<br />\nACO: 每日一般6點前走人,每星期返44小時,很少OT,OT都可以報,放工唔洗諗公司野<br />\nIT\t:每日一般7-8點左右走人,常常OT,仲要晚上隨時收call support,check email<br />\n<br />\n到40中<br />\nACO :應該升一級上CO(pt16-21), CO人工近40K(40K係未計通脹 每年再加幾%,40*(1.03)^20),工作如常 幾年換一次位, 好似22日假,強積金供出面好多,又可以申請公屋居屋,不用擔心住屋醫療<br />\nIT人 :工作如常 OTOT, IT人多數合約工 好少福利...開始outdated,跟唔上後生, 除時被炒又搵工,租屋比較安全<br />\n<br />\n到50中<br />\nCO好運升上SCO人工50K左右(未計通脹 每年再加幾%),安守本份,不會比人炒,等到65歲退休.福利照舊 不怕經濟起伏<br />\n<br />\nIT人,晉升不明朗,可能經過被炒N次 已轉行,市場上新職位中意請FG, 人工變動好大,可能都係落手落腳前線位 ,少數可能上到管理職位<br />\n<br />\n到65歲<br />\nCO/SCO :光榮退休 服務政府大眾40年,有好既退休保障(每個月供既(25+5)%強積金,退休就一大筆)<br />\nIT :不知道<br />\n<br />\nACO睇落普普通通 但做左20年既人到中年後一般都會有40-50K(計埋通脤),<br />\n20年到就排隊升CO又多萬幾<br />\n<br />\n1.唔會怕中年失業,可以keep住升職and加人工<br />\n2.可以住緊用公務員隊申請既公屋, 唔洗煩住屋問題 <br />\n3.有14日升到2X日假,請假又唔難批<br />\n4.每月有2X+5%強積金幫你供 <br />\n5.朝9晚6少OT,就算要OT都可似claim返 <br />\n6.唔洗擦鞋保住份工,有理既可以話返上司轉頭<br />\n7.放工唔洗keep住進修,怕比後生取代<br />\n8.work life balance,放工就放工去邊玩,照顧屋企人就得唔會比工作搞到冇曬私人時間<br />\n9.幾年換一次位,有好有唔好,但唔洗一世做同一個位同一樣野<br />\n10.一年2次加人工 1.通脹2.升pt<br />\n11.2公婆都係ACO既 人到中年10萬8萬月入實有<br />\n12.唔會好似IT咁 讀書又一班仔,做野又一班仔,女都唔易識 ,到中年要供樓,養仔女時跟唔上時代轉變 失業就慘<br />\n<br />\n2A3O officer,AP2 , EO ,紀律部隊更加比做IT 有前途,2x-4xK既起薪<br />\npoint 22 以上好似仲可以申請供樓資助,約10年 每月有幾K 至 1X K<br />\n真正做左政府工,就明白有幾好 同穩定 安全 唔會怕 中年失業連住屋都有問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T01:31:54.000Z","msg":"香港呢個社會真係變撚態<br />\n迫個個走去做正苦工<br />\n其他行業點樣發展?<br />\n社會點會進步?<br />\n正苦只會高價賣地<br />\n助長高價賣樓<br />\n只要有錢/稅收<br />\n理撚得其他行業死活<br />\n真係短視到仆街<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b54249d4d2e4cc8347208feeb5ddb39fc2e6f33a","tid":569460,"uid":98317,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T01:37:32.000Z","msg":"做IT預左要讀成世書，我唔係話叫返學校讀書，而係一出新既techni book/ documentations 就要花時間去浸<br />\n我對上個SA寫左廿年java, js一出，react 啲library 三個月就完全上晒手，反而教返啲新仔點寫<br />\n但人地係日日放工就自己睇書做lab, 所以搞到成40歲人都冇女朋友<br />\n入行之前問下自己有冇絕子絕孫既覺悟先"},{"pid":"84f43fa4973b3f7e614f6ea4a091b0cb8a47ce40","tid":569460,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T04:54:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/125430_8589a2f2867060cb87dd1e6304f02ff6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F125430_8589a2f2867060cb87dd1e6304f02ff6.png&h=ea5d1869&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a1cd3cb2be199b4e0191b9da574fd69d6438a83","tid":569460,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84f43fa4973b3f7e614f6ea4a091b0cb8a47ce40","tid":569460,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T04:54:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/125430_8589a2f2867060cb87dd1e6304f02ff6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F125430_8589a2f2867060cb87dd1e6304f02ff6.png&h=ea5d1869&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T05:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6daad083951ed46682646bc5ffc9860dc2049ba9","tid":569460,"uid":49144,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:12:04.000Z","msg":"做 IT <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 命都冇<img src=\"/asset